          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-9">
            <h3 style="color: #3787ad;">Inhaler education - does it make a difference?</h3>
            <p>9<sup>th</sup> September 2015 at 12.30-13.15</p>
            <p>Join Monica Fletcher, Chief Executive of Education for Health, as she provides an overview of inhaler education in asthma patients, specifically regarding the effect of this education on outcomes. This presentation will follow-on from the previous two webinars in the series, which will discuss unmet needs for adequate treatments and the use of the PRIMIS asthma care audit tool.</p>
